reviews.review_text:
A leaf of all colors plays a golden string fiddle I've heard various recordings of this show and this one is not to shabby..I was there and remember the crowd going nuts for the Casey Jones and thinking this is gonna be a goodie..and it was~! Anyone who has attended Grateful Dead shows a Merriweather understands how special the place was. During intermission I was hanging out tripping balls and a guy came up with a big smile and handed me a card..it read. "Annie Beauneu from Saint Angel say,
"The weather down here so fine" Black Peter Restoration Society..and than he ran off. It was shit like that which kept this freak coming back..GIVE IT A WHIRL..Forever Grateful>Forever Dead
